data.description: Great floor plan boasts four bedrooms to provide enough space for the whole family! Spacious split bedroom plan, eat-in kitchen, huge living room that can be combined with dining, recently remodeled bathroom, septic field lines were replaced three years ago, fenced backyard with plenty of room to play! Conveniently located  close to Chattanooga, TN and Fort Oglethorpe, GA. Large front porch. Attached carport. Laundry room is huge and doubles as a mud room, and holds potential for another full bath or extra closet space in the master. Mountain views!
